# Ignore everything by default
*

# Allow directories so we can unignore files inside them
!*/

# Allow all Python files anywhere in this folder tree
!**/*.py

# Keep this .gitignore tracked
!.gitignore

# Notes:
# - This will prevent non-.py files (including secret key files) from being tracked.
# - If you already committed secrets (e.g. `bedrock api key` or `github access token`),
#   you'll need to remove them from the index (see commands below).